    <item>
      <title>伊拉克努力在190亿美元的亏损后恢复石油流向土耳其</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-15/iraq-works-to-resume-oil-flows-to-turkey-after-19-billion-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[外交大臣说，伊拉克正在努力解决半自治的库尔德地区政府的技术问题，以重新启动向土耳其的原油出口管道，此前将近两年的停工使伊拉克损失了约190亿美元的收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-15/iraq-works-to-resume-oil-flows-to-turkey-after-19-billion-loss</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Feb 2025 14:41:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
